[23:18.20]	+ FERDINAND following]
[23:18.65]	ARIEL'S song.
[23:20.08]	Come unto these yellow sands,
[23:22.70]	And then take hands:
[23:24.65]	Courtsied when you have and kiss'd
[23:27.72]	The wild waves whist,
[23:29.75]	Foot it featly here and there;
